            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1313.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>potatoes</strong> and <strong>sprouts</strong> are cooked, drain and return them to the pot</p><p>Return the pot to a low heat and add a splash of <strong>milk</strong> and a large knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Mash until smooth – this is your <strong>sprout mash</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
